Package: okeanos.quantmod.interface
Type: Package
Title: Set of wrappers around the mighy quantmod packge that adapt its functionalities
    for more regular market screening based on yahoo data.
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Artur Wegrzyn
Maintainer: Artur Wegrzyn <awegrzyn17@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains a set of classes and functions that serve the 
    purpose of analysing selected time series (fetched chiefly via quantmod) and checking
    them for the occurrences of trade signals. Additionally, a customized Twitter
    communication protocol is provided so that the signals check results can be 
    published there.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
